---

---

<section
    class="med-section med-section-local"
>
    <div class="med-absolute med-inset-0 med-pointer-events-none med-opacity-10">
        <svg class="med-w-full med-h-full">
            <pattern
                id="magneticField"
                x="0"
                y="0"
                width="50"
                height="50"
                patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse"
            >
                <path
                    d="M 10 25 Q 25 10 40 25"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#38bdf8"
                    stroke-width="1"
                    opacity="0.5"></path>
                <path
                    d="M 10 35 Q 25 50 40 35"
                    fill="none"
                    stroke="#38bdf8"
                    stroke-width="1"
                    opacity="0.5"></path>
            </pattern>
            <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#magneticField)"></rect>
        </svg>
    </div>

    <div class="med-container">
        <div class="med-grid">
            <div class="med-info-column">
                <span
                    class="med-tag med-tag-local"
                    >La Fuerza Invisible</span
                >
                <h2 class="med-title med-title-local">La Brújula</h2>

                <p class="med-description med-description-local">
                    Durante milenios, nos guiamos por lo que veíamos: el sol y las estrellas. Pero,
                    ¿qué haces cuando el cielo está nublado?
                </p>

                <div
                    class="med-card med-card-local"
                >
                    <h3 class="med-card-title med-card-title-local">El Pez que Señala al Sur</h3>
                    <p class="med-card-text med-card-text-local">
                        Los chinos descubrieron que cierta piedra "amaba" al hierro. Una aguja
                        magnetizada, flotando en agua, siempre buscaba el Norte.
                    </p>
                    <p class="med-card-note med-card-note-local">
                        No medía la distancia ni el tiempo. Medía la dirección de una fuerza que
                        nadie podía ver ni explicar.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="med-visual-column med-visual-column-local">
                <div class="med-visual-wrapper">
                    <svg viewBox="0 0 400 400" class="med-w-full med-h-full med-overflow-visible">
                        <g opacity="0.3">
                            <circle
                                cx="200"
                                cy="200"
                                r="140"
                                fill="none"
                                stroke="#94a3b8"
                                stroke-width="1"></circle>
                            <path
                                d="M 200 60 L 200 340 M 60 200 L 340 200"
                                stroke="#94a3b8"
                                stroke-width="1"
                                stroke-dasharray="4 4"></path>
                            <text
                                x="200"
                                y="50"
                                text-anchor="middle"
                                fill="#38bdf8"
                                font-weight="bold">N</text
                            >
                            <text x="200" y="360" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8">S</text>
                            <text x="350" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8">E</text>
                            <text x="50" y="205" text-anchor="middle" fill="#94a3b8">O</text>
                        </g>

                        <g class="animate-compass-needle">
                            <path
                                d="M 200 100 L 220 200 L 200 300 L 180 200 Z"
                                fill="#1e293b"
                                stroke="#cbd5e1"
                                stroke-width="2"></path>

                            <path d="M 200 100 L 220 200 L 180 200 Z" fill="#ef4444"></path>

                            <circle
                                cx="200"
                                cy="200"
                                r="8"
                                fill="#f1f5f9"
                                stroke="#64748b"
                                stroke-width="2"></circle>
                        </g>

                        <g opacity="0.2" stroke="#38bdf8" fill="none" stroke-width="2">
                            <path d="M 100 400 Q 0 200 100 0"></path>
                            <path d="M 300 400 Q 400 200 300 0"></path>
                        </g>
                    </svg>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .med-section-local {
        background-color: #0f172a;
        color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .med-tag-local {
        color: #38bdf8;
        border-color: #0ea5e9;
    }

    .med-title-local {
        color: #f0f9ff;
    }

    .med-description-local {
        color: #bae6fd;
        opacity: 0.9;
    }

    .med-card-title-local {
        color: #7dd3fc;
    }

    .med-card-text-local {
        color: #e2e8f0;
    }

    .med-card-note-local {
        color: #38bdf8;
    }

    .med-visual-column-local {
        height: 400px;
    }

    .med-card-local {
        background-color: color-mix(in srgb, #1e293b 50%, transparent);
        border-color: #0ea5e9;
    }

    @keyframes compassNeedle {
        0% {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
        20% {
            transform: rotate(10deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
        40% {
            transform: rotate(-5deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
        60% {
            transform: rotate(2deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
        80% {
            transform: rotate(-1deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
        100% {
            transform: rotate(0deg);
            transform-origin: 200px 200px;
        }
    }
    .animate-compass-needle {
        animation: compassNeedle 6s ease-in-out infinite;
    }
</style>
